sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Open profile modal
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/profile
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    API->>DB: Load user profile
    DB-->>API: Profile data
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + profile
    Frontend-->>User: Display profile form
